title: Great American Cleanup/Make a Difference Day (Township of Anderson, OH)
text: ( Source : Township of Anderson , OH) Pick Up Trash / Plant A Tree This Week ! The Great American Cleanup is set from 8:30 a.m. to noon on Saturday, Oct. 24. Volunteers meet at Anderson Center , 7850 Five Mile Road, to pick up their assignments
